{{Infobox Union|<!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. --> |name= UDA |country= [[Canada]] |affiliation= [[International Federation of Actors|FIA]] |members= 6900 |full_name= Artist Union |native_name= Union des artistes |image= [[Image:Union des artistes logo.png|150px]] |founded= |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= |people= [[Sophie Prégent]], president |website= [http://www.uniondesartistes.com www.uniondesartistes.com] |footnotes= }} The '''Union des artistes''' (UDA) or '''Artist union''' is a [[Quebec]]-based labour organization representing stage, television, radio and film performers in French-language media in Canada (the English language labour organization is [[ACTRA]]). It represents over 6,900 members and is affiliated with the [[International Federation of Actors]] (FIA). The current president is [[Sophie Prégent]].
